/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T01:31:05.000Z","msg":"估計係演出效果啫<br />\n一黎鄭中基自己時不時都拎呢件事自抽，<br />\n二黎米奇輩份高咁多，鄭中基正常都唔會發作。<br />\n<br />\n我反而記得有次狄娜做嘉賓，佢做司儀，狄娜批評佢司儀唔得正經咁，佢居然當眾抽呀狄娜以前拍豔情片（呢條片cctbb好似有擺上YouTube），好小家。"},{"pid":"0f767268d970861a2644b161dad08fd05537b04f","tid":2424722,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T01:33:41.000Z","msg":"邊有人睇香港節目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大陸浪姐都冇人睇啦"},{"pid":"59308a17fa75c8af8b05454c6449550aa52c93e5","tid":2424722,"uid":277578,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T01:54:30.000Z","msg":"佢咁矮坐得耐啲人以為佢嗰日冇返工。不了。"},{"pid":"7458e409c07c94b401a55091bf015bcd09159631","tid":2424722,"uid":8257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46153a8160ce4483d806faaee8ba58507fb7319b","tid":2424722,"uid":222907,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b0562cff9e77ef6d1343237611d52dbc100112d2","tid":2424722,"uid":134683,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T23:11:37.000Z","msg":"佢口臭到黐線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有一次佢、鄭中基同唔記得邊個同台做司儀<br />\n曾志偉夠膽死當眾串鄭中基喺飛機上飲醉酒打人嗰件事<br />\n鄭中基即刻着L左咁想郁佢<br />\n好彩有第三個司儀㩒住中基同打圓場<br />\n如果唔係可能直播佢兩個打交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T00:04:51.000Z","msg":"鄭中基地位邊夠佢黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你話成龍我就信"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T02:02:37.000Z","msg":"你當佢老豆死？"},{"pid":"8069adb3a21e0b24e24dd1b6f6d8334424d138a4","tid":2424722,"uid":137569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"17e5951647c1584d2871896f66ff3a03854aecbb","tid":2424722,"uid":254813,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T00:12:31.000Z","msg":"佢已經得罪蔡康年啦！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T03:33:07.000Z","msg":"叫大屍祝